{"tid":96516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[B乜鳩]英國金融時報,SWIFT:人民幣退居全球第六大支付貨幣","createTime":"2017-01-27T01:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T05:46:42.000Z","uid":28934,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a084e51aa3e4da7d5c2f7eefb46202b5f61d5dc","tid":96516,"uid":28934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T01:59:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>SWIFT：人民幣退居全球第六大支付貨幣</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001071183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001071183&d=4nIA3IbJeVg%2FUN0DUWkZ0Av3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=e505a9d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001071183</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n8.cmsfile.pg0.cn/group1/M00/2C/56/Cgqg11atWtmALi_MAAIRsVQ96BM731.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn8.cmsfile.pg0.cn%2Fgroup1%2FM00%2F2C%2F56%2FCgqg11atWtmALi_MAAIRsVQ96BM731.jpg&h=d8e81b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSWIFT發布的新數據顯示，2016年人民幣國際使用量大幅下滑，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">資本管制</span></strong>和美元走強削弱了人民幣的吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n更新於2017年1月26日 17:48 英國《金融時報》 米強 北京報道 <br />\n<br />\n周四發布的新支付數據顯示，2016年人民幣國際使用量大幅下滑，資本管制和美元走強削弱了人民幣的吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n環球同業銀行金融電訊協會(SWIFT)表示，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">與2015年相比，人民幣國際支付額下滑了29.5%。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n在2016年各幣種國際使用量排行榜上，人民幣僅排在第六位，盡管去年10月人民幣被國際貨幣基金組織(IMF)正式承認為全球儲備貨幣之一。其他儲備貨幣包括美元、歐元、日元和英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QaahYiA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQaahYiA.gif&h=5c1b13b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n021m2L.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn021m2L.gif&h=37498e67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnZFX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnZFX.gif&h=2ab738a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2015年人民幣在該榜單上排在第五位，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今年取代人民幣位子的是加元</span></strong>。加元並不包含在IMF特別提款權(SDR)貨幣籃子中。<br />\n<br />\n人民幣在SWIFT榜單上的排名下滑，是北京方面擱置人民幣國際化野心的最新跡象，中國央行已轉而把主要精力放在抑制人民幣對美元貶值和中國外匯儲備持續縮水上。自2014年以來，中國外匯儲備已縮水25%，至3萬億美元。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;中國央行短期內的重心已從人民幣國際化轉到讓人民幣外流和人民幣匯率企穩上，&rdquo;中國社會科學院的張明表示，&ldquo;我預計2017年將繼續實施資本管控，人民幣對美元將緩慢貶值。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nSWIFT支付市場亞洲主管邁克爾‧穆恩(Michael Moon)還把人民幣國際使用量下滑歸因於中國經濟增長放緩。去年中國經濟產出增長6.7%，是25年來年增速最慢的一年。<br />\n<br />\n但穆恩預計，隨著建立起更多的離岸人民幣清算中心，人民幣的使用量將會反彈。中國監管部門也表示，近期出台的資本管控是臨時性措施。"},{"pid":"25f687150bac5cf61b9781ea14d808ff315b6fd3","tid":96516,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd3933a46d5fbd96d9cd3fb7af19d3107d9aba1","tid":96516,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1347809b5282e38b5b0ba66aaad2ee50c6b73614","tid":96516,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"你唔比人滙出美元人地點樣可以結算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e2ccc0f0f9b908a493171193bd0a1f9c918a03","tid":96516,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T18:15:46.000Z","msg":"加紙都大過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b26ae6c882205f24ff186916db8f6bef150d64","tid":96516,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T18:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5c6c97db0d8a4b2f4f2c8e697187b3695320cb","tid":96516,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T22:56:22.000Z","msg":"真正支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c62783a19dcd3180c6b2ffc425cb24f6d6f3120","tid":96516,"uid":57376,